videos.description: Michigan almost lost the ball on three separate occasions in the same possession, but after gaining control, Joe Teske makes the open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Michigan avoids a turnover 3 times before nailing the jumper

videos.description: Jordan Poole gets the outlet pass on the fast break and throws it down on the defender for the basket and the foul.
videos.headline: Poole slams on defender for and-1 dunk
